│ dominance check before returning the result of `isBasicBlockEntryGuardedByCond`.\n\n### 5. │
│ Conclusion ###\nThe proposed fix ensures that the `evaluatePredicateAt` function only      │
│ evaluates the predicate in valid contexts, preventing incorrect transformations in         │
